"This hadith has been transmitted thus by 'Umar b. Khattab (with a slight change of words):\" I heard Hisham b. Hakim reciting Surah al-Furqan during the lifetime of Allah's Messenger (ﷺ).\" The rest is the same but with this addition:\" I was about to catch hold of him in prayer, but I exercised patience till he pronounced salutation"